{"tid":1698520,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（抵制TVB）Nivea妮維雅落CCTVB廣告 絲打們仲買唔買？","createTime":"2019-11-07T14:13:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-08T13:20:32.000Z","uid":75759,"like":34,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"827ac07cae39135f372b9c7e613ee0e0654a95ab","tid":1698520,"uid":75759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T14:13:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />罷買，支持黃色經濟圈<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我係港豬<br />\n<br />\n各位marketing JJ注意，<br />\nTVB係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>品牌負資產</strong></span></span>，喺TVB落廣告，<br />\n你哋苦心經營嘅<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">品牌形象將付諸流水</span></span></strong>！無人可憐！<img src=\"/assets/faces/husky/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nTVB今個月開始同廣告客戶傾下年合約，Keep住個氣勢到年底啦！<br />\n廣告界多番強調，去FB洗版係有用ga<br />\n<br />\n是晚重溫@7 Nov 2019 <br />\nNivea<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/nivea.hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fnivea.hk%2F&d=Z9XWEpuBYzNDjlwSEAyqK6CH8iT5eEApQhURqQe1KTk%3D&h=8326fba8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/nivea.hk/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YseN4LY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYseN4LY.jpg&h=fcc58302&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【Nivea做咩？】<br />\nNivea d 產品係幾平，好多學生都鐘意用<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但佢係CCTVB 落廣告真係好趕客<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nTarget年輕人市場大把marketing channel 可以揀<br />\n點解要落人見人憎既CCTVB 呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/husky/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望Nivea 可以好似佢地2008年雪糕事件咁，見有唔妥好收喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nNivea雪糕事件<img src=\"/assets/faces/husky/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">2008年5月22日，高登會員「賽特」，於高登討論區發表《請大家免費食ok軟雪糕》[1]帖子後，吸引了大量會員回覆。\n\n該主題附有一條鏈結，前往止汗劑生產商Nivea所舉辦的網上問答遊戲，參與者需要回答數條問題，才能得以下載並列印OK軟雪糕換領贈券。\n\n由於有太多人以免費雪糕贈券在「OK便利店」換取雪糕，結果令多間OK便利店聲稱雪糕機出現故障。有些分店不是沒有甜筒存貨，就是已經售罄。在數天內，有不少「OK便利店」的分店甚至已經停售雪糕。[4]\n\n有網民發文表示，有些使用贈券的個別中學生，甚至一次過換領多筒軟雪糕，因吃不完便丟棄部分軟雪糕，反而造成浪費。[5]\n\n在2008年5月26日，NIVEA網頁上表示「反應空前熱烈」，故贈券已派發完畢[6]。\nhttps://bit.ly/36axJOo</code></pre><br />\n<br />\n當年Nivea都識cut單保平安，唔知佢會唔會低能到學某件伍氏臭X放棄兩代年輕人，繼續落廣告去人見人憎TVB呢。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />讓我們繼續看下去。<br />\n<br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可！<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>再唔撤budget，業績定仆直！盡快同TVB割席！</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n#Nivea #妮維雅 #黃色經濟圈<br />\n<br />\n【抵制CCTVB 任務流程】<br />\n1.派嬲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2.洗版<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n3.罷買<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />請用幾秒去派嬲、留言、推post <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />俾幾秒我哋抵制TVB團隊得唔得? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n※請善用template，清晰表達訴求<br />\n無綫新聞，歪曲事實，出賣港人！本人明白貴公司或已簽訂今年合約，未能即時撤回廣告，故暫時罷用。請貴公司承諾不簽訂2020 TVB廣告合約，不以無綫藝人代言，否則將列入「永久抵制名單」，永不錄用。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SguqRrx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSguqRrx.jpg&h=e210ca4c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n記得bookmark: TVB廣告客戶名單！！ <br />\n消費前諗清楚 <br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2P7cPeD\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2P7cPeD&d=Z9XWEpuBYzNDjlwSEAyqK6CH8iT5eEApQhURqQe1KTk%3D&h=9149f118\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2P7cPeD</a> <br />\n－－－－－－－ <br />\n請即follow: <br />\nFB: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/sayno2tvb\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fsayno2tvb&d=Z9XWEpuBYzNDjlwSEAyqK6CH8iT5eEApQhURqQe1KTk%3D&h=a8f342a1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/sayno2tvb</a><br />\nIG: #sayno2tvb<br />\nTG: <a href=\"https://t.me/sayno2tvb\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fsayno2tvb&d=Z9XWEpuBYzNDjlwSEAyqK6CH8iT5eEApQhURqQe1KTk%3D&h=a6e87293\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/sayno2tvb</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>多謝大家</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32524549429ec24ca5a9cb45304747e97b0f50c7","tid":1698520,"uid":164752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T14:14:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04327f5f0146ffdf7729c29b33cc822b4996ed5b","tid":1698520,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T14:14:33.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: orange;\">求幫推</span><br />\n<br />\n（求手動置頂）英國戰線Twitter要人！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1698490\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1698490</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"a7de2314b4ff96f0cc102b464276d91ce20ac4bf","tid":1698520,"uid":146535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T14:15:04.000Z","msg":"係咪集中推呢個"},{"pid":"adb684ac5f3c16145c776d83dce14ed2e5b6f15c","tid":1698520,"uid":78392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T14:18:16.000Z","msg":"做咩連開2個"},{"pid":"3d210a9275531b2d0cfc9b417f9a04fb08894f81","tid":1698520,"uid":78392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T14:18:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmo